abstractText: Tally of Large Woody Debris (LWD) pieces in a reach, number of pieces by channel location, number of pool forming wood pieces, number of pieces that are part of a log jam, and the number of key pieces. LWD data collection methodology follows a customized approach of Method ID: 4069, described in Protocol ID: 1875 and Protocol ID: 1880.
title: Large Woody Debris Counts v1.0
